title: UC Football Heads to E8 Rival St. John Fisher Saturday (Greater Utica Chamber of Commerce) ...
text: ( Source : Greater Utica Chamber of Commerce ) The Utica College football team hits the road for the second away game in as many weeks against Empire 8 Conference foe St. John Fisher College on Saturday. Kickoff is scheduled for 1 p.m. Time
